"```sql\nSELECT client.client_id, \n       (strftime('%Y', 'now') - strftime('%Y', client.birth_date)) - \n       (strftime('%m-%d', 'now') < strftime('%m-%d', client.birth_date)) AS age\nFROM client\nINNER JOIN disp ON client.client_id = disp.client_id\nINNER JOIN card ON disp.disp_id = card.disp_id\nWHERE card.type = 'gold' AND disp.type = 'OWNER';\n```"